body.description: FDS Intimate + Body Cleansing in Coconut Milk is a two-in-one feminine wash that’s gentle enough to use daily on your intimate areas and strong enough to cleanse the rest of your body without stripping away your skin’s natural moisture. The pH-balanced body wash cleanses in harmony with the natural chemistry of your intimate areas, providing a gentle clean. This moisturizing body wash has been gynecologist and dermatologist tested, so you can feel confident about adding it to your stock of feminine hygiene products. The exotic aroma of this coconut body wash whisks you away to a tropical beach with every inhale. Plus, the creamy cleansing formula of this vaginal wash includes no dyes, alcohol, soaps or other harsh drying ingredients, helping maintain your skin's natural moisture while washing away odor. Trust this feminine care formula to leave you smelling fresh all day long after you step out of the shower for confidence from head to heels.
